---
title: Curried Puff Pie with Roasted Sweet Potato, Onion and Lentils
description: Our Curried Puff Pie is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R43_W02_UK_V17037-6_Main_high-ea0b47df.jpg
